	   <tr><td colspan=2>Im sorry but at higher levels do not follow this guide.  First of all, when fighting an enchanter, you will have the dominance physically and mentally.  Enchanters at higher levels know they cant PK worth crap and will most likely avoid confrontation.  Also, if they do fight you, they will not waste time charming your pet, they will just fear it because fear takes less time to cast and lower mana.<br>When fighting a necro, i would suggest using a fire pet because it attacks quickly and casts its nuke more frequently than the air pets stun.  This amount of damage being taken will cause the necro to try to run or cause a laps in which u can nuke him to death.<br>At higher levels, mages are possibly the best PvP class solo.  Dont get me wrong tho.  If you are fighting a necro or druid, chances are you will die after the fight if you dont have a healer, but you will prolly have killed them first.  Due to our high powered nukes and our own little warriors, we have the upper hand in most fights.<br><br>Zahr D'crullo<br>experienced PvP mage<br>Vallon-Zek<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
